name: EGOTRIPS X ZUZ DUFFEL BAG "SAILOR'S ZEC"
description:
ZEC  | ZUZ - EGOTRIPS - COLLABORATION 

The collaboration between Egotrips Clothing and ZUZ developed out of our mutual friendship and the fact that we adore her quality handmade bags!
As a result, we have launched a capsule collection - consisting of a gym bag and a duffel bag - which feature Egotrips‘ graphic artwork and Zuza‘s amazing skills in designing and sewing.


"Sailor`s ZEC"

- 100% Durable Canvas Outer 
- Canvas Lining with Flower Print
- Draw String Closure with Golden Grommet
- Hook-And-Loop Fastener to adjust Size 
- Triangular Reinforced Bottom for more Stability
- French Seaming
- Cotton Rope Shoulder Strap
- Screen Printed 

...
